- Annotates the Lifecycle Diagram with a second warning: execute the edge as an ATOMIC SWAP (add one, remove both siblings, one `gh issue edit`).
- Adds a brief plan-review-discipline meta-note (resolve to a SINGLE concrete plan with cited `file:line` + code + named tests, not reviewer-self-critique bullets) — explicitly cross-referenced to the existing `*-before-planning` skills to avoid duplication; recorded only because it shaped this fix.
